import React from 'react'
import { StepNavDiv, OneThirdDiv } from './step-lower-nav.styles'

export default function StepLowerNav() {
    return (
        <StepNavDiv>
            <OneThirdDiv>
                STEPS
            </OneThirdDiv>
            <OneThirdDiv>
                INFO
            </OneThirdDiv>
            <OneThirdDiv>
                LOG
            </OneThirdDiv>
        </StepNavDiv>
    )
}
